    "title": "Marketplace Manager - Reliance Digital - Apply Now",
    "description": "An exciting career opportunity awaits you at Reliance Digital. We are on the lookout for a dedicated Marketplace Manager to strengthen our Gurgaon-based team.\n\nAbout Reliance Digital:\nReliance Digital is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Manage customer reviews, ratings, and return/refund processes\n• Execute digital marketing campaigns across Google, Meta, and other channels\n• Optimize product pages for search visibility and conversion\n• Create engaging content for product pages and social media\n• Build and maintain affiliate and influencer marketing programs\n• Track key performance indicators including GMV, conversion rate, and ROI\n• Coordinate with vendors and suppliers for inventory management\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Sc / M.Sc in Life Sciences\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Google Analytics\n• Proficiency in Performance Marketing\n• Proficiency in Affiliate Marketing\n• Proficiency in Data Analytics\n• Proficiency in CRM Software\n• Proficiency in A/B Testing\n• Proficiency in Facebook Ads\n• Proficiency in Magento\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Referral bonus program\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Flexible working hours\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Gurgaon, Haryana, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Reliance Digital!",
